
AutoOps AI — Intelligent Incident Management Platform
Overview
AutoOps AI is an AI-inspired incident management platform built using UiPath. The system dynamically processes operational incidents, identifies remediation actions through a knowledge base engine, stores incident history, detects recurring failures, and generates analytics dashboards for operational visibility.
________________________________________
Key Features
•	Dynamic incident processing
•	Knowledge-based remediation engine
•	Persistent incident memory
•	Recurring incident detection
•	Operational analytics dashboard
•	Autonomous remediation selection
•	Executive operational visibility
________________________________________
