•	UiPath Studio
•	Excel Automation
•	DataTables
•	LINQ
•	Dashboard Analytics
•	Workflow Orchestration
________________________________________
Architecture Components
1.	Incident Source Layer
2.	UiPath Processing Engine
3.	Knowledge Base Engine
4.	Autonomous Remediation Layer
5.	Incident Memory Store
6.	Analytics Engine
7.	Dashboard & Alerts
________________________________________
Business Value
The platform helps operations teams reduce manual monitoring effort, identify recurring operational failures, improve remediation visibility, and create a scalable intelligent operations workflow.
